  • Constructor Details

    • PartyBus

      public PartyBus(SportsBus s, int barArea)
      Represents a PartyBus, which is a specialized type of SportsBus, designed to accommodate social events. It extends the SportsBus class and adds an attribute for the bar area.
      Parameters:
      s - the SportsBus object containing shared attributes
      barArea - the area designated for the bar within the bus
